Entries.default: "Best not to touch anything until we know what's going on here."
"These are Readceran soldiers. Dyrwoodan, too. Is this from the Saint's War?"
"Should we not stand still as well, captain?"
"Ishi, try and leave the dead in peace."
"I think that soldier's Readceran. That one, too."
"This architecture - it appears to be of the Eastern Reach. And the blood... it's too still."
"This place stinks of flame and flesh. Don't suppose we could leave?"
"A bridge to nowhere from nowhere. Complanca, what is next?"
"Thought it sure as hel couldn't get any weirder than an undead dragon. Call me a fool."
